317
00:31:32,891 --> 00:31:33,892
And Tanner.

318
00:31:34,017 --> 00:31:36,436
One and two and three.

319
00:31:36,561 --> 00:31:38,688
And one, and two, and three.

320
00:31:39,231 --> 00:31:41,483
And one, and two and three...

321
00:31:54,454 --> 00:31:56,373
This is shit.

322
00:31:57,874 --> 00:32:00,210
- Such shit.
