337
00:32:32,284 --> 00:32:33,994
She wanted to live her beliefs.

338
00:32:34,119 --> 00:32:35,996
Who doesn't admire that?

339
00:32:36,121 --> 00:32:39,833
And there's so much to change
in the world.

340
