to her room, please, Tanner?

346
00:33:00,687 --> 00:33:02,355
No, Miss Tanner!

347
00:33:03,815 --> 00:33:05,525
Call Olga a cab.

348
00:33:05,650 --> 00:33:07,402
She's had enough.

349
00:33:07,527 --> 00:33:09,821
And is going to pack her things

350
00:33:09,946 --> 00:33:13,074
