the protagonist?

354
00:33:44,981 --> 00:33:47,359
Sonia?

355
00:33:47,484 --> 00:33:49,903
I can't. Not yet.

356
00:33:50,028 --> 00:33:51,696
Caroline?

357
00:33:55,575 --> 00:33:57,869
Very well. We'll manage.

358
00:33:57,994 --> 00:34:01,540
