448
00:48:45,381 --> 00:48:47,508
I went once by bus,

449
00:48:47,633 --> 00:48:50,136
then I hitchhiked the other two.

450
00:48:50,261 --> 00:48:52,555
That's risky.

451
00:48:52,680 --> 00:48:54,932
Were you punished?

452
00:48:56,016 --> 00:48:57,560
Yeah.

453
00:48:58,644 --> 00:49:00,980
