the protagonist in Volk.

479
00:51:05,688 --> 00:51:09,316
I didn't think it was
gonna be like this.

480
00:51:09,441 --> 00:51:12,236
She's so kind.

481
00:51:12,361 --> 00:51:14,363
That's wonderful.

482
00:51:17,992 --> 00:51:19,827
Are you all right?

483
00:51:21,453 --> 00:51:24,665
I'm fine. I was just...

484
00:51:27,042 --> 00:51:30,296
